name: I´M HAPPY ´CAUSE U ARE HERE
description:
Don´t worry so much and be kind.

Say hello to those you don´t know and give them a welcome to your land.

We have to be together to undestand how to live better.

I was walking around Jaipur, in India and this happened to me: thousands of people recibing me happly.

I was missing home at that time, but i start to feel that a bigger one was borning.
